      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张紫艳上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00002",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "索南枝",
      "speakers": [
        "张紫艳"
      ],
      "text": "如簧口心性乔，牢笼计成兴祸苗。蓦地假妆着，潜行透出风声杳。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00003",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张紫艳"
      ],
      "text": "奴家张紫艳。因见贺芳谗言，要害秦将军性命，因此奴家呵！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00004",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "索南枝",
      "speakers": [
        "张紫艳"
      ],
      "text": "夤夜间不惮途路遥，怕逢人识奴旧貌。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00005",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张紫艳"
      ],
      "text": "这里已是营门首了。有人么？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00006",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "将官上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00007",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "将官"
      ],
      "text": "上府传金札，前军拥铁衣。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00008",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "将官"
      ],
      "text": "是哪个？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00009",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "将官见。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00010",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张紫艳"
      ],
      "text": "奉大王钧旨，要见秦将军。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00011",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "将官"
      ],
      "text": "请少待。老爷有请！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00012",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦琼上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00013",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "令严鼓角三更静，夜宿貔貅万灶炊。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00014",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "将官"
      ],
      "text": "大王钧旨，有差官要见。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00015",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "道有请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02005028_e00016",
      "play_id": "02005028",
      "scene_id": "02005028_s01",
